                "Tool Tip": {
                    "Type": 5.0,
                    "String": ""
                },
                "Caption": {
                    "Type": 5.0,
                    "String": "Non-energy revenue and expenses are cash flow inputs not correlated with kWh of energy or kW of capacity. These variables affect EBITDA and are available for debt service. The retained and paid percenteges are intended to represent revenue and cost sharing agreements with other legal entities. In Value mode, SAM applies both inflation and escalation to the first year cost to calculate out-year costs. In Schedule mode, neither inflation nor escalation applies. See Help for details."
                },
